title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 2 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 2 2021
description:
Creepy new New York governor says God sent the vaccine to smart people, prepares to fire health care workers who won't get the shot. Axios poll: Majority doesn't trust Biden. Clay and Buck in Tuscaloosa this weekend. NBA players Jonathan Issac, Bradley Beal stand up for freedom from vaccine mandates. Places with high vaccination rates are seeing record covid hospitalizations. Nurse will walk away from 30-year career rather than get vaccine.
